ED_Title: Cooperation between the United Nations and the Organisation for Economic Co-operation and Development (OECD)
ED_DecisionText: At its 95th plenary meeting, on 5 September 2025, the General Assembly decided to include the sub-item entitled “Cooperation between the United Nations and the Organisation for Economic Co-operation and Development (OECD)” of the item entitled “Cooperation between the United Nations and regional and other organizations” in the draft agenda of its eighty-first session.
